ent%20by%20encouraging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiming-retirement-older-americans-delay-if-possible-recession-economic-uncertainty-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearlier%20and%20earlier%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Continuing%20to%20work%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20contributes%20to%20a%20person's%20%26quot%3Bfeeling%20of%20worth%26quot%3B%20and%20being%20interested%20and%20engaged%20in%20%26quot%3Bwhat's%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20sure%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20probably%20will%20feel%20much%20better%20by%20working%20longer%2C%20and%20the%20economy%20will%20be%20stronger%2C%26quot%3B%20Malkiel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20government%20should%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-age-denmark-raised-70-pensions-workers-unions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20the%20retirement%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bvery%20gradually%26quot%3B%C2%A0and%20predicted%20that%20this%20might%20be%20necessary%20to%20avoid%20bankrupting%20the%20Social%20Security%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219492502-2b96-4e82-a5ca-c4100c34b593%5C%22%3EWhat%20keeps%20him%20awake%20at%20night%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20kept%20him%20up%20at%20night%2C%20Malkiel%20chuckled%20and%20said%20his%20Cavapoo%2C%20Lucy%2C%20who%20was%20barking%20in%20the%20background.%20He%20described%20her%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhellion%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20sweet%26quot%3B%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnswering%20the%20question%20less%20literally%2C%20Malkiel%20said%20he's%20a%20%26quot%3Bcard-carrying%20Republican%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20still%20%26quot%3Bquite%20concerned%26quot%3B%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20actions%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20tariffs%20woul