-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etwo%20less%20generous%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20go%20into%20effect%20next%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20restarted%20interest%20charges%20on%20SAVE%20balances%20on%20August%201%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eafter%20a%20yearlong%20pause.%20This%20means%20Smith%20and%20the%208%20million%20other%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20can%20either%20switch%20to%20a%20new%20plan%20and%20likely%20face%20higher%20monthly%20payments%20or%20remain%20on%20SAVE%20for%20now%20and%20watch%20their%20balances%20grow.%20Smith%20said%20that%20she%20asked%20her%20servicer%20for%20an%20estimate%20on%20her%20interest%20charges%2C%20and%20she%20was%20told%20it%20would%20be%20about%20%24468%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20vote%20for%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20Trump%20supporter%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20things%20I%20don't%20really%20agree%20with%2C%20and%20this%20is%20one%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20Smith%20said%20her%20payments%20were%20around%20%24150.%20Federal%20Student%20Aid's%20loan%20simulator%20predicted%20that%20her%20payments%20could%20surge%20to%20nearly%20%241%2C000%20off%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20which%20Smith%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20cannot%20afford.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20heard%20from%20dozens%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20who%20are%20concerned%20about%20interest%20charges%20restarting%20and%20eventually%20having%20to%20move%20to%20a%20different%20repayment%20plan.%20Some%20borrowers%20are%20balancing%20their%20agreement%20with%20Trump%20that%20loans%20should%20be%20repaid%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20financial%20strain%20that%20comes%20with%20losing%20SAVE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20education%20secretary%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20announcing%20the%20interest%20charges%20restart%20that%20the%20administration%20is%20focused%20on%20%26quot%3Bstrengthening%20the%20student%20loan%20portfolio%20and%20simplifying%20repayment%20to%20better%20serve%20borrowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20this%20effort%2C%20the%20Department%20urges%20all%20borrowers%20in%20the%20SAVE%20Plan%20to%20quickly%20transition%20to%20a%20legally%20compliant%20repayment%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20Income-Based%20Repayment%20Plan%2C%26quot%3B%20McMahon%20said.%20%26quot%3BBorrowers%20in%20SAVE%20cannot%20access%20important%20loan%20benefits%20and%20cannot%20make%20progress%20toward%20loan%20discharge%20programs%20authorized%20by%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20is%20hoping%20she'll%20be%20able%20to%20cover%20the%20interest%20charges%2C%20but%20she%20doesn't%20have%20a%20plan%20for%20potentially%20much%20higher%20payments%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20struggle.%20I%20do%20agree%20we%20have%20to%20pay%20them%2C%20but%20it's%20really%20hurting%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20shame.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20spoken%20with%20dozens%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20grappling%20with%20changes%20to%20debt%20relief%20and%20repayment%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20emailing%20asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20and%20read%20more%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHow%20Trump's%20big%20spending%20bill%20will%20overhaul%20repayment%20for%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-react-default-collections-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMillions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20are%20about%20to%20be%20thrown%20into%20collections.%20Some%20say%20they're%20already%20'barely%20scraping%20by.'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-retirement-default-collections-risk-social-security-checks-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStudent-loan%20debt%20followed%20them%20into%20retirement.%20Now%20it%20threatens%20their%20Social%20Security%20checks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-borrowers-react-debt-relief-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EA%20new%20threat%20to%20public%20servants'%20key%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20has%20them%20on%20edge%3A%20'I'm%20so%20close%20to%20the%20finish%20line'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd4ab848-c5ce-40d2-9f1a-9df02d068c7d%5C%22%3E'A%20wait%20and%20see%20game'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Krull's%20goal%20is%20to%20pay%20off%20his%20student-loan%20balance.%20He%20was%20never%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20repayment%2C%20and%20he%20wants%20a%20concrete%20plan%20to%20fit%20monthly%20student-loan%20payments%20into%20his%20budget.%20The%20constantly%20changing%20student-loan%20policies%20make%20that%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20trying%20to%20cheat%2C%20we're%20not%20trying%20to%20not%20pay%20our%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20Krull%2C%2042%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20take%20care%20of%20our%20responsibilities.%20We%20just%20want%20a%20system%20in%20place%20that%20we%20can%20rely%20on%20and%20be%20able%20to%20financially%20plan%20for%20our%20futures%20and%20endeavors%20that%20exist%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrull%20went%20back%20to%20school%20in%20his%20late%2020s%20on%20the%20pre-law%20track%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20earning%20a%20law%20degree%2C%20but%20his%20priorities%20changed.%20He%20got%20married%20and%20had%20children%2C%20and%20once%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20retail%20manager%20and%20now%20works%20in%20operations%20at%20a%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20qualified%20for%20%240%20monthly%20payments%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20and%20he's%20been%20unable%20to%20get%20an%20estimate%20of%20his%20new%20payment%20on%20a%20different%20repayment%20plan.%20He%20plans%20to%20see%20how%20much%20interest%20starts%20building%20on%20his%20balance%20and%20determine%20at%20that%20point%20whether%20it%20makes%20the%20most%20sense%20for%20him%20to%20remain%20on%20SAVE%20and%20pay%20off%20the%20interest%20or%20take%20action%20to%20get%20on%20a%20new%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20the%20uncertainty%20is%20taking%20a%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20I'm%20playing%20a%20wait-and-see%20game%20and%20making%20the%20move%20that%20makes%20the%20most%20sense%20financially%20once%20I%20can%20determine%20what%20those%20finances%20are%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Krull%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20he's%20worried%20he'll%20have%20to%20scale%20back%20on%20his%20retirement%20and%20health%20savings%20should%20his%20payments%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlannah%20is%20in%20a%20similar%20boat.%20Working%20in%20public%20health%2C%20she%20said%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20halved%20her%20payments%20from%20around%20%24800%20a%20month%20to%20just%20over%20%24400%2C%20which%20allowed%20her%20to%20put%20more%20money%20into%20savings%20and%20put%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20house.%20The%20uncertainty%20with%20SAVE%20has%20been%20frustrating%2C%20she%20said%2C%20because%20she%20planned%20her%20budget%20around%20her%20lower%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20she%20heeded%20the%20administration's%20advice%20and%20submitted%20an%20application%20to%20switch%20to%20an%20income-based%20repayment%20plan%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20but%20she%20said%20the%20application%20is%20still%20processing%2C%20keeping%20her%20in%20limbo.%20The%20Department%20of%20Education%20also%20posted%20a%20notice%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-paused-ibr-trump-halts-borrower-debt-relief-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eloan%20forgiveness%20through%20IBR%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20paused%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlannah%20said%20she%20plans%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20making%20any%20student-loan%20payments%20until%20she%20has%20certainty%20that%20the%20plan%20she%20is%20on%20will%20count%20toward%20debt%20relief.%20She%20said%20that%20if%20she%20paid%20off%20her%20loans%20aggressively%2C%20she%20would%20run%20through%20her%20savings%20%E2%80%94%20and%20be%20left%20with%20nothing%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c596bdde-8309-4375-ab82-d7b947f3510a%5C%22%3E'Everything%20right%20now%20is%20backlogged'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20to%20SAVE%20come%20as%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20itself%20is%20undergoing%20a%20major%20overhaul.%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20begin%20dismantling%20the%20department%2C%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20ruled%20that%20the%20agency%20can%20proceed%20with%20firing%201%2C400%20workers%2C%20about%20half%20of%20its%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcMahon%20said%20following%20the%20ruling%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20win%20for%20students%20and%20families%26quot%3B%20and%20allows%20the%20department%20the%20%26quot%3B%20authority%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20staffing%20levels%2C%20administrative%20organization%2C%20and%20day-to-day%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20leaves%20the%20department%20with%20fewer%20resources%20to%20manage%20major%20tasks%2C%20including%20creating%20a%20new%20repayment%20system%20and%20processing%20millions%20of%20borrowers'%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20Holly%20Atkinson%2C%20a%2057-year-old%20nurse%20who%20voted%20for%20Trump%2C%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20such%20a%20hot%20mess%20over%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Atkinson%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20right%20now%20is%20backlogged%20as%20it%20is%2C%20and%20if%20they%20lay%20off%20these%20people%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20make%20the%20situation%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtkinson%20said%20she%20was%20enjoying%20low%20monthly%20payments%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20before%20it%20was%20blocked.%20With%20her%20repayment%20future%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%20she's%20now%20unsure%20if%20she'll%20ever%20be%20able%20to%20retire%20with%20student%20loans%20hanging%20over%20her%20head%2C%20while%20also%20managing%20a%20separate%20private%20student-loan%20balance%20and%20mortgage%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20feel%20like%20it's%20a%20weight%20on%20my%20shoulder%20that's%20never%20going%20to%20get%20lifted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20see%20people%20my%20age%20planning%20to%20retire%20and%20go%20on%20vacations%20and%20travel%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20see%20any%20of%20that%20happening%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20it%20would%20be%20communicating%20with%20SAVE%20borrowers%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months%20regarding%20their%20options%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan.%20Atkinson%20wishes%20there%20was%20more%20clarity%20upfront.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20regret%20voting%20for%20him%2C%20but%20what%20I'm%20seeing%20right%20now%20makes%20me%20very%20uncomfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20Atkinson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20all%20in%20limbo%20right%20now%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20like%20being%20in%20limbo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-fear-higher-payments-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754208542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688a1ae13d5881a51c1e3e53%3Fform