analyst%20expectations%20over%20the%20past%20two%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20change%20like%20this%20is%20difficult%20and%20can%20be%20unsettling%20for%20some%2C%26quot%3B%20Stankey%20said%20in%20the%20memo.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20as%20General%20Eric%20Shinseki%20so%20eloquently%20stated%2C%20'If%20you%20dislike%20change%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20dislike%20irrelevance%20even%20more.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a3fe4ba-6ea1-4cfe-ba85-967c36124d85%5C%22%3ERead%20AT%26amp%3BT%20CEO%20John%20Stankey's%20full%20memo%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Message%20from%20John%20Stankey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20Observation%20on%20our%20Employee%20Survey%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20All%20AT%26amp%3BT%20Managers%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThank%20you%20to%20the%20over%2099%2C000%20employees%20who%20responded%20to%20this%20year's%20Employee%20Survey.%20Your%20feedback%20helps%20us%20understand%20what%20we%20need%20to%20focus%20on%E2%80%94and%20how%20we%20need%20to%20communicate%20%E2%80%94%20as%20we%20strive%20toward%20our%20goal%20of%20ranking%20in%20the%20top%20third%20of%20Fortune%20100%20companies%20in%20employee%20engagement.%20%3Cstrong%3EIt%20is%20incredibly%20encouraging%20that%2073%25%20of%20our%20employees%20took%20the%20time%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20survey%2C%20with%2079%25%20of%20those%20respondents%20feeling%20committed%20and%20engaged%20with%20their%20work%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT.%20While%20this%20is%20reassuring%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20amount%20of%20change%20we've%20navigated%20as%20a%20company%20recently%2C%20it%20wasn't%20a%20surprise%20to%20me%20that%20we%20fell%20short%20of%20our%20engagement%20goal.%20Nor%20was%20it%20a%20surprise%20that%20scores%20declined%20since%20our%202023%20survey.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20are%20midstream%20on%20a%20multi-year%20journey%20to%20build%20the%20company%20we%20want%2C%20not%20simply%20optimize%20the%20one%20we%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20believe%20your%20feedback%20accurately%20reflects%20where%20we%20are.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIn%20the%20survey%20you%20asked%20for%20transparency%20in%20communication%20from%20leadership.%20Although%20not%20my%20best%20in%20terms%20of%20brevity%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20multi-page%20note%20is%20to%20share%20a%20few%20of%20my%20thoughts%20with%20you%20directly%20while%20your%20leaders%20work%20with%20you%20to%20prepare%20their%20action%20plans.%20After%20reading%20this%2C%20I'm%20hopeful%20you%20will%20understand%20my%20perspective%20on%20the%20company%20we%20are%20working%20to%20build%20and%20what%20we%20can%20and%20will%20do%20to%20respond%20to%20elements%20of%20your%20feedback.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThis%20note%20may%20also%20help%20you%20identify%20areas%20where%20your%20professional%20expectations%20might%20be%20misaligned%20with%20the%20strategic%20direction%20of%20this%20company.%20Most%20points%20outlined%20below%20have%20been%20communicated%20in%20other%20forums%20and%20with%20your%20leadership%2C%20but%20this%20is%20my%20attempt%20to%20articulate%20how%20all%20the%20pieces%20fit%20together.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ELet%20me%20start%20by%20setting%20some%20context%20on%20what%20has%20been%20underway%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT%20over%20the%20last%204%20years.%20%3Cstrong%3ETo%20secure%20our%20long-term%20success%20as%20a%20company%2C%20we%20concluded%20that%20a%20shift%20in%20our%20operating%20culture%20was%20essential.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20those%20of%20you%20who%20are%20fans%20of%20management%20science%2C%20this%20shift%20can%20be%20characterized%20as%20moving%20away%20from%20an%20orientation%20on%20hierarchy%20and%20familial%20cultural%20norms%20and%20towards%20a%20more%20externally%20focused%20and%20competitive%20market-based%20culture.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20understand%20that%20some%20of%20you%20may%20have%20started%20your%20tour%20with%20this%20company%20expecting%20an%20%26quot%3Bemployment%20deal%26quot%3B%20rooted%20in%20loyalty%2C%20tenure%2C%20and%20conformance%20with%20the%20associated%20compensation%2C%20work%20structure%2C%20and%20benefits.%20We%20have%20consciously%20shifted%20away%20from%20some%20of%20these%20elements%20and%20towards%20a%20more%20market-based%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20focused%20on%20rewarding%20capability%2C%20contribution%2C%20and%20commitment.%20We%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20dynamic%2C%20technologically%20driven%20markets%20where%20we%20operate.%20I%20know%20change%20like%20this%20is%20difficult%20and%20can%20be%20unsettling%20for%20some.%20However%2C%20as%20General%20Eric%20Shinseki%20so%20eloquently%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20dislike%20change%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20dislike%20irrelevance%20even%20more.%26quot%3B%20Many%20of%20your%20survey%20comments%20indicate%20agreement%20with%20this%20notion%20%E2%80%94%20a%20desire%20for%20our%20company%20to%20evolve%20to%20better%20support%20our%20customers%20and%20each%20other.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIf%20you%20are%20of%20the%20small%20minority%20that%20shared%20comments%20similar%20to%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20heard%20this%20nonsense%20before%20and%20I'll%20ignore%20things%20until%20this%20goes%20away%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bthings%20were%20just%20fine%20the%20way%20they%20were%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20there%20might%20be%20a%20disconnect%20between%20you%20and%20your%20current%20professional%20choice.%20It%20takes%20every%20one%20of%20us%2C%20moving%20in%20the%20same%20direction%2C%20to%20win%20against%20the%20competition%2C%20sustain%20our%20business%2C%20and%20create%20rewarding%20and%20interesting%20challenges%20for%20employees%20who%20want%20to%20work%20in%20a%20market-based%20culture.%20Changes%20to%20compensation%2C%20pensions%2C%20benefits%20(paid%20time%20off%2C%20care%20leaves%2C%20mental%20health%20support)%2C%20delayering%2C%20work%20locations%2C%20and%20workplace%20environment%20are%20all%20in%20service%20of%20this%20change.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhen%20I%20read%20comments%20lamenting%20disruption%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20pick%20my%20brain%20for%20an%20example%20of%20another%20100%2B%20year%20old%20company%20that%20didn't%20have%20to%20disrupt%20itself%20to%20secure%20sustainable%20relevance.%20I%20am%20still%20searching%20for%20the%20first%20example.%20I%20suspect%20our%20willingness%20to%20disrupt%20ourselves%20is%20the%20under-pinning%20of%20why%20this%20company%20approaches%20150%20years%20of%20relevance%20%E2%80%94%20from%20fixed%20to%20mobile%2C%20TDM%20(Time%20Division%20Multiplexing)%20to%20IP%20(Internet%20Protocol)%2C%20and%20narrowband%20to%20broadband%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20I%20recall%20at%20every%20turn%20there%20were%20parts%20of%20the%20organization%20advocating%20to%20maintain%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20and%20I%20suspect%20hindsight%20would%20tell%20us%20we%20are%20happy%20we%20chose%20change%20%E2%80%94%20as%20messy%20as%20the%20journey%20might%20have%20been.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20Survey%20Feedback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ENow%20to%20the%20survey.%20There%20was%20quite%20a%20bit%20to%20unpack%20in%20your%20feedback%2C%20but%20like%20any%20business%20imperative%2C%20focus%20and%20prioritization%20are%20essential.%20Your%20collective%20data%20and%20comments%20were%20analyzed%20to%20extract%20the%20most%20critical%20themes%20outlined%20in%20this%20note.%20You%20will%20hear%20more%20specifics%20from%20your%20respective%20leaders%20around%20these%20themes%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Career%20and%20professional%20growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20agree%20with%20the%20sentiment%20that%20everyone%20should%20understand%20potential%20career%20opportunities%20and%20career%20paths%20we%20have%20here%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT.%20With%20that%2C%20you%20should%20have%20a%20solid%20sense%20of%20the%20contribution%20required%20in%20your%20current%20role%2C%20and%20what%20can%20be%20done%20to%20earn%20more%20responsibility%20to%20push%20professional%20pursuits%20to%20a%20higher%20level.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMany%20leaders%20have%20not%20yet%20fully%20addressed%20this%20expectation%20within%20their%20own%20organizations.%20Our%20shift%20to%20hub%20locations%20was%20a%20pivotal%20step%20to%20more%20effectively%20achieve%20this%20goal.%20Concentrations%20of%20employees%20enables%20the%20teamwork%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20visibility%20that%2C%20when%20combined%20with%20performance%20and%20contribution%2C%20can%20better%20equip%20you%20to%20advance%20your%20career.%20While%20we%20have%20made%20strides%20to%20get%20more%20people%20into%20fewer%20places%2C%20we%20have%20more%20work%20to%20do%20to%20align%20complimentary%20work%20functions%20in%20the%20right%20places.%20I%20expect%20all%20department%20leaders%20to%20complete%20this%20work%20%E2%80%94%20to%20thoughtfully%20consolidate%20coordinating%20functions%20and%20career%20paths%20to%20reduce%20the%20ongoing%20need%20to%20relocate%20for%20growth%20and%20development.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Capabilities%20to%20do%20your%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20deserve%20tools%2C%20processes%2C%20and%20capabilities%20that%20help%20you%20serve%20our%20customers%20effectively%2C%20without%20being%20hindered%20by%20internal%20process%20friction%20or%20system%20constraints.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhile%20we've%20made%20progress%20with%20legacy%20migrations%20and%20infrastructure%20upgrades%2C%20there's%20still%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%20We%20find%20ourselves%20at%20the%20midpoint%20in%20what%20is%20a%20long%20and%20technically%20challenging%20journey.%20You%20have%20my%20commitment%20that%20improving%20these%20capabilities%20remains%20a%20top%20priority.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20allocating%20resources%20and%20attention%20to%20ensure%20we%20see%20tangible%20benefits%20of%20our%20record%20levels%20of%20investment%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20and%20we'll%20continue%20to%20update%20you%20on%20these%20improvements.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Where%20we%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20right%20to%20expect%20to%20work%20in%20a%20professional%2C%20well-maintained%2C%20and%20functional%20facility.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnother%20reason%20we%20established%20a%20focused%20set%20of%20hubs%20was%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20invest%20in%20our%20workplaces%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20a%20more%20common%20standard.%20This%20was%20something%20we%20never%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20while%20operating%20in%20500%2B%20metropolitan%20areas.%20It's%20also%20why%20we%20need%20to%20continue%20exiting%20under-utilized%20real%20estate%20(the%20remnants%20of%20deferred%20maintenance%20from%20a%20long%20string%20of%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions)%20to%20free%20up%20resources%20to%20invest%20in%20our%20core%20locations.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20fact%20is%20real%20estate%20transitions%20require%20sustained%20efforts%20over%20several%20years%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20place%20we%20desire%20and%20you%20deserve.%20Some%20of%20you%20are%20in%20a%20location%20where%20enhancements%20are%20actively%20underway%20or%20even%20completed.%20Others%20may%20be%20unaware%20of%20changes%20that%20are%20coming%20in%20short%20order.%20We%20will%20more%20actively%20share%20where%20we%20are%20making%20investments%2C%20what%20has%20been%20accomplished%2C%20and%20what%20is%20on%20the%20horizon.%20We%20agree%20with%20the%20feedback%20you%20shared%2C%20and%20we%20are%20taking%20this%20seriously.%20I%20expect%20we%20all%20will%20be%20required%20to%20demonstrate%20some%20patience%20and%20flexibility%20as%20we%20work%20towards%20a%20better%20place.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Culture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EYour%20collective%20comments%20about%20culture%20may%20be%20the%20most%20difficult%20to%20synthesize.%20This%20topic%20is%20a%20bit%20like%20beauty%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20all%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20beholder.%20Many%20of%20you%20suggest%20a%20desire%20to%20improve%20upon%20what%20you're%20observing%20as%20%26quot%3Bdaily%20norms.%26quot%3B%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20summarize%20a%20set%20of%20actions%20that%20could%20quickly%20guarantee%20our%20transition%20to%20the%20market-based%20cultural%20norms%20I%20described%20earlier.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20a%20short-term%20list%20of%20actions%20or%20programs%20would%20suffice.%20Believe%20me%2C%20there%20is%20nobody%20more%20impatient%20for%20this%20outcome%20than%20yours%20truly.%20Changing%20and%20embracing%20a%20workplace%20culture%20is%20like%20learning%20a%20language%20%E2%80%94%20knowledge%20grows%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%20and%20develops%20over%20time.%20Like%20learning%20a%20language%2C%20you%20gain%20proficiency%20by%20practicing%20in%20the%20real%20world.%20We%20need%20to%20commit%20to%20learning%20the%20language%20together%20so%20we%20can%20all%20share%20a%20common%20%26quot%3Bshorthand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20we%20will%20be%20doing%20some%20additional%20work%20illustrating%20what%20market-based%20culture%20norms%20look%20like%20in%20practice%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sharing%20some%20prompts%20that%20can%20be%20applied%20in%20your%20daily%20work%20life.%20%3Cstrong%3EWe'll%20keep%20coming%20at%20this%20cultural%20evolution%20from%20every%20angle%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20have%20to%20ask%20you%20to%20commit.%20Commit%20to%20adjusting%20your%20own%20behaviors%20and%20actions%20without%20looking%20to%20your%20right%20or%20left%20(or%20above)%20to%20see%20what%20everybody%20else%20is%20doing.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20favorite%20quote%20by%20W.%20Clement%20Stone%20comes%20to%20mind%3A%20%26quot%3BSo%20many%20fail%20because%20they%20don't%20get%20started.%26quot%3B%20Please%20jump%20in%20and%20avoid%20the%20human%20tendency%20to%20blame%20the%20neighbors%20for%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20neighborhood!%20We%20will%20all%20change%20at%20a%20slightly%20different%20pace%2C%20and%20that's%20to%20be%20expected.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Personal%20wellbeing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20understand%20that%20many%20may%20find%20the%20demands%20of%20your%20daily%20lives%20challenging%20and%20difficult.%20Elder%20care%2C%20job%20stress%2C%20child%20rearing%20challenges%2C%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20community%20unrest%2C%20technology%20anxiety%20%E2%80%94%20the%20list%20can%20get%20long.%20%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20no%20company%20can%20address%20how%20the%20combination%20of%20these%20dynamics%20might%20impact%20your%20specific%20circumstances%2C%20we%20can%20work%20to%20support%20employees%20in%20a%20way%20that%20improves%20their%20ability%20to%20manage%20what%20life%20throws%20at%20them.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOur%20decisions%20to%20maintain%20industry-leading%20healthcare%2C%20change%20time-off%20policies%2C%20augment%20leave%20structures%2C%20offer%20financial%20counseling%2C%20and%20enhance%20mental%20health%20benefits%20are%20examples%20of%20overt%20decisions%20we%20have%20made%20on%20this%20front.%20Despite%20rising%20medical%20costs%2C%20we%20intend%20to%20hold%20management%20medical%20contributions%20flat%20for%20the%202026%20renewal%20cycle.%20We%20continue%20to%20test%20new%20approaches%20to%20services%20and%20care%20in%20the%20workplace%20and%20are%20seeing%20some%20promising%20models%20emerge%20that%20may%20warrant%20implementing%20at%20scale.%20These%20are%20just%20some%20examples%20of%20how%20we%20are%20constantly%20evaluating%20how%20we%20can%20best%20support%20you%20in%20managing%20life%20dynamics%2C%20and%20you%20can%20expect%20more%20updates%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ENow%2C%20onto%20some%20additional%20context%20and%20expectation%20setting.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20work%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20most%20challenging%20things%20we%20do%20here%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT%20require%20unwavering%20teamwork%20-%20it's%20essential%20that%20we%20attract%20and%20promote%20talent%20that%20embraces%20working%20together%20to%20deliver%20results.%20When%20you%20think%20about%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20to%20transform%20this%20company%20-%20efforts%20like%20legacy%20sunset%2C%20fiber%20deployment%2C%20wireless%20network%20modernization%2C%20moving%20down%20market%20in%20Business%2C%20BSS%2FOSS%20(Business%20Support%20System%2FOperations%20Support%20System)%20platform%20migrations%2C%20digital%2Fonline%2Fomni%20channel%20enablement%2C%20core%20routing%20network%20consolidation%2C%20and%205G%20standalone%20core%20-%20these%20are%20all%20efforts%20that%20require%20inter-departmental%20collaboration%20and%20coordination.%20They%20constitute%20the%20bulk%20of%20our%20%2423%20billion%20annual%20investment.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThis%20work%20is%20far%20more%20demanding%20and%20challenging%20than%20our%20efforts%20to%20keep%20the%20train%20on%20the%20tracks%20during%20enforced%20COVID%20isolation.%20-person%20collaboration%20and%20predictable%20presence%20improves%20each%20team's%20ability%20to%20execute%20effectively%20on%20large%2C%20complex%20projects.%20Our%20customers%20expect%20us%20to%20be%20here%20to%20serve%20their%20needs.%20Our%20third-party%20partners%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20consistently%20depend%20on%20times%20to%20collaborate.%20Our%20employees%20deserve%20reliable%20support%20with%20their%20current%20responsibilities%20and%20impromptu%20guidance%20for%20continued%20development.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20work%20in%20person%2C%20together%2C%20during%20common%20hours.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20run%20a%20dynamic%2C%20customer-facing%20business%2C%20tackling%20large-scale%2C%20challenging%20initiatives.%20If%20the%20requirements%20dictated%20by%20this%20dynamic%20do%20not%20align%20to%20your%20personal%20desires%2C%20you%20have%20every%20right%20to%20find%20a%20career%20opportunity%20that%20is%20suitable%20to%20your%20aspirations%20and%20needs.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20a%20self-directed%2C%20virtual%2C%20or%20hybrid%20work%20schedule%20is%20essential%20for%20you%20to%20manage%20your%20career%20aspirations%20and%20life%20challenges%2C%20you%20will%20have%20a%20difficult%20time%20aligning%20your%20priorities%20with%20those%20of%20the%20company%20and%20the%20culture%20we%20aim%20to%20establish.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EDoes%20this%20mean%20there%20isn't%20room%20for%20emergencies%20or%20special%20circumstances%3F%20Of%20course%20not.%20will%20always%20try%20to%20support%20that%20which%20can't%20be%20planned%20for%20%E2%80%94%20or%20that%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20deliberately%20planned%20for%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20expect%20any%20leader%20to%20manage%20their%20organization%20accordingly.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EContribution%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20effectiveness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOur%20cultural%20tenants%20include%20our%20intent%20to%20Win%20as%20One.%20Implicit%20in%20this%20commitment%20to%20one%20another%20is%20that%20we%20all%20carry%20our%20part%20of%20the%20load%20aid%20measurably%20contribute%20to%20the%20priorities%20the%20team.%20As%20technology%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Binformation%20economy%26quot%3B%20evolves%2C%20each%20of%20our%20respective%20contributions%20are%20going%20to%20become%20increasingly%20measurable.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIn%20addition%20to%20information%20garnered%20from%20performance%20reviews%2C%20peer%20feedback%2C%20assessments%20work%20history%2C%20and%20certifications%20(to%20name%20a%20few)%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Ewe%20analyze%20patterns%20of%20behaviors%20from%20broad%20cohorts%20(aggregated%20data).%20This%20allows%20leaders%20to%20identify%20behaviors%20that%20are%20obvious%20outliers%2C%20supplemented%20with%20the%20broadest%20set%20of%20information%20available%2C%20to%20determine%20if%20the%20behavior%20being%20evaluated%20is%20consistent%20with%20our%20stated%20priorities%20and%20employment%20expectations.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAn%20employee's%20data%20must%20significantly%20differ%20from%20their%20peers%20%E2%80%94%20to%20a%20level%20harming%20team%20cohesion%2C%20compensation%2C%20and%20inconsistent%20with%20our%20Win%20as%20One%20philosophy%20%E2%80%94%20before%20an%20individual's%20name%20is%20linked%20to%20any%20behavior.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ESome%20may%20view%20this%20approach%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20trust%2C%20and%20that%20perspective%20is%20understandable.%20In%20several%20forums%2C%20I've%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20past%20data%20indicated%20more%20outliers%20than%20we'd%20like.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIf%20we%20overlook%20these%20outliers%2C%20it%20can%20impact%20overall%20trust%20in%20leadership%20and%20coworkers%2C%20especially%20among%20those%20who%20consistently%20contribute%20and%20uphold%20our%20standards.%20Addressing%20these%20exceptions%20is%20important%20to%20ensure%20we're%20fair%20to%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20employees%20who%20support%20their%20colleagues%20and%20deliver%20for%20the%20organization%20every%20day.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3ENext%20steps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20hope%20this%20clarifies%20how%20we've%20prioritized%20action%20planning%20around%20your%20feedback%20%E2%80%94%20and%20transparently%20explains%20why%20some%20concerns%20and%20desires%20expressed%20may%20not%20be%20entirely%20aligned%20with%20our%20strategic%20direction%20as%20a%20company.%20While%20it's%20natural%20to%20feel%20uneasy%20during%20times%20of%20conflict%20and%20change%2C%20the%20greatest%20source%20of%20lasting%20anxiety%20is%20when%20expectations%20aren't%20aligned%20or%20discussed%20openly.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EDetermining%20the%20best%20way%20to%20address%20new%20challenges%20and%20position%20the%20company%20for%20long-term%20success%20is%20constantly%20on%20our%20minds%20as%20leaders.%20I%20truly%20believe%20that%20this%20approach%20is%20the%20way%20to%20attract%20and%20retain%20customers%2C%20secure%20necessary%20resources%20from%20our%20investors%2C%20and%20offer%20meaningful%20employment%20to%20as%20many%20of%20our%20folks%20as%20possible.%20As%20difficult%20as%20it%20is%20to%20balance%20all%20these%20stakeholders%2C%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20we%20are%20on%20the%20right%20track.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EYour%20leadership%20team%20will%20be%20outlining%20our%20path%20forward%20in%20response%20to%20the%20survey%20in%20more%20detail.%20Until%20then%2C%20I%20ask%20that%20each%20of%20you%20explore%20your%20own%20opportunities%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%20While%20there%20will%20certainly%20be%20actions%20and%20initiatives%20that%20require%20sponsorship%20from%20senior%20leaders%2C%20our%20collective%20success%20also%20depends%20on%20each%20of%20us%20taking%20ownership%20where%20we%20can.%20Rather%20than%20waiting%20for%20others%20to%20act%2C%20I%20encourage%20everyone%20to%20share%20their%20ideas%20and%20take%20initiative.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAs%20I%20said%20at%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20are%20midstream%20on%20a%20multi-year%20journey%20to%20build%20the%20company%20we%20want%2C%20not%20simply%20optimize%20the%20one%20we%20have.%20%3Cstrong%3EYour%20feedback%20makes%20us%20better%2C%20and%20we%20have%20many%20strong%20capabilities%20and%20attributes%20to%20leverage.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20best%20days%20are%20ahead.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EJohn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20from%20a%20non-work%20email%20and%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adreuter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edreuter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20on%20Signal%20646.768.4750%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cd