ider.com%2Fflew-premium-economy-norse-airlines-upgrade-worth-it-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backlash%20to%20Delta's%20AI%20pricing%20shows%20the%20tightrope%20companies%20walk%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224945%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Delta%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6881314f85e81483682e8d46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223297%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDelta%20said%20it's%20using%20AI%20to%20set%20prices.%3Cp%3ERonen%20Tivony%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDelta%20was%20met%20with%20swift%20backlash%20when%20it%20said%20it%20was%20ramping%20up%20its%20plans%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20set%20fares.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20showed%20a%20challenge%20companies%20face%20with%20satisfying%20shareholders%20and%20consumers%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndustry%20experts%20said%20AI%20adoption%20requires%20transparency%20and%20a%20focus%20on%20improving%20the%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-premium-select-worth-it-business-class-alternative-long-flight-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelta%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20said%20it%20was%20ramping%20up%20its%20use%20of%20AI%20to%20set%20fares%2C%20the%20backlash%20from%20customers%20was%20swift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20demonstrated%20a%20common%20problem%20companies%20face%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%3A%20how%20to%20adopt%20new%20technology%20(and%20brag%20about%20it%20to%20please%20shareholders)%20without%20freaking%20out%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20has%20said%20it%20is%20not%20using%20AI%20to%20set%20different%20prices%20for%20different%20individuals%20based%20on%20their%20personal%20data.%20Instead%2C%20the%20airline%20says%20AI%20is%20being%20used%20to%20improve%20existing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-dynamic-pricing-inflation-costs-china-trade-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edynamic%20pricing%20%3C%2Fa%3Epractices%20that%20are%20already%20used%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20fare%20product%20Delta%20has%20ever%20used%2C%20is%20testing%2C%20or%20plans%20to%20use%20that%20targets%20customers%20with%20individualized%20offers%20based%20on%20personal%20information%20or%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20were%20still%20spooked.%20Online%2C%20they%20complained%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-prices-inflation-soaring-corporate-greed-profits-margins-wages-jobs-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprice%20gouging%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20lawmakers%20sent%20a%20letter%20demanding%20answers%20from%20Delta%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20data%20privacy%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20price%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20very%20dystopian%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Brent%20McDonald%2C%20a%20lawyer%20based%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20and%20a%20frequent%20Delta%20flyer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20McDonald%20said%20in%20cities%20like%20Salt%20Lake%2C%20which%20is%20a%20major%20hub%20for%20Delta%2C%20there%20are%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20options%20for%20direct%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20that%20monopoly%20power%2C%20it%20could%20be%20very%20abusive%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20maximize%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20they'll%20get%20from%20each%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Sanders%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20research%20insights%20at%20G2%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20say%20you%20have%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20a%20consumer%20product%2C%20it%20raises%20red%20flags%20with%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20tend%20to%20love%20it%20since%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20efficiency%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelta%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20impress%20its%20investors%2C%20stepped%20into%20a%20PR%20backlash%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc614c07-3514-451e-b8ab-e9b942d78731%5C%22%3EConsumers%20don't%20trust%20AI%2C%20so%20messaging%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20experts%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20said%20Delta's%20lack%20of%20details%20in%20its%20initial%20public%20discussions%20of%20using%20AI%20led%20some%20consumers%20to%20worry%20about%20potential%20worst-case%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Investor%20Day%20in%20November%2C%20Delta%20said%20about%201%25%20of%20its%20network%20had%20fares%20set%20using%20AI.%20Delta%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-premium-seats-economy-cabin-profit-investor-day-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGlen%20Hauenstein%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20initial%20results%20show%20amazingly%20favorable%20unit%20revenues%26quot%3B%20and%20that%2C%20eventually%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20have%20a%20price%20that's%20available%20on%20that%20flight%2C%20on%20that%20time%20to%20you%2C%20the%20individual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-hits-record-profits-airline-stocks-bounce-on-luxury-demand-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta's%20second-quarter%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20call%20in%20July%2C%20Hauenstein%20said%20AI%20was%20now%20being%20used%20to%20set%20prices%20on%20about%203%25%20of%20its%20domestic%20network%20and%20that%20the%20goal%20was%20to%20get%20to%2020%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20heavy%20testing%20phase%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20like%20what%20we%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-airlines-ai-pricing-ruben-gallego-letter-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESen.%20Ruben%20Gallego%3C%2Fa%3E%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Delta%20requesting%20answers%20about%20its%20AI%20pricing%2C%20the%20airline%20responded%20and%20said%20much%20of%20what%20was%20being%20said%20about%20their%20process%20was%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20letter%20presupposes%20that%20we%20are%20using%2C%20and%20intend%20to%20use%2C%20AI%20for%20'individualized'%20pricing%20or%20'surveillance'%20pricing%2C%20leveraging%20consumer-specific%20personal%20data%2C%20such%20as%20sensitive%20personal%20circumstances%20or%20prior%20purchasing%20activity%20to%20set%20individualized%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20July%2031.%20%26quot%3BTo%20clarify%2C%20this%20is%20incorrect%2C%20and%20this%20assumption%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20has%20created%20confusion%20and%20misinformation%20in%20the%20public%20discourse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20also%20shared%20more%20details%20about%20how%20it's%20using%20AI.%20The%20airline%20said%20AI%20is%20assisting%20human%20analysts%20by%20forecasting%20demand%20for%20specific%20routes%2C%20aggregating%20purchasing%C2%A0data%2C%20and%20factoring%20in%20thousands%C2%A0of%20variables%20at%20once%20%E2%80%94%20though%20not%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESanders%20said%20being%20transparent%20about%20how%20AI%20is%20being%20used%20could%20help%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20consumer%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20companies%20should%20look%20toward%20the%20transparency%20practices%20at%20AI%20industry%20leaders%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-safety-policy-gpt4-1-employee-criticism-musk-lawsuit-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20he%20noted%20has%20introduced%20features%20that%20have%20ChatGPT%20show%20its%20work%20and%20explain%20its%20reasoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20airlines%20could%20do%20that%20would%20be%20to%20show%20fare%20factors%20on%20its%20ticket%20prices%2C%20or%20to%20provide%20some%20explanation%20about%20how%20a%20price%20was%20set.%20He%20also%20said%20airlines%20could%20allow%20users%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20AI-priced%20seats%20and%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20could%20mean%20some%20seats%20may%20not%20be%20offered%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d729b07b-d04e-4803-80c6-0464557a8ed6%5C%22%3ECompanies%20should%20talk%20about%20how%20they're%20using%20AI%20to%20improve%20their%20service%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClint%20Henderson%2C%20managing%20editor%20at%20the%20travel%20website%20The%20Points%20Guy%2C%20said%20he's%20worried%20that%20AI%20being%20used%20in%20pricing%20could%20actually%20lead%20airlines%20to%20penalize%20their%20most%20loyal%20customers%20by%20upcharging%20them%20because%20they%20will%20pay%20more%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20airline%20and%20get%20the%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaas-ai-changing-how-software-companies-charge-customers-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20pricing%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20potentially%20be%20used%20for%20good%2C%20too%2C%20like%20by%20giving%20a%20discount%20to%20a%20new%20customer%20or%20offering%20cheaper%20upgrades%20to%20first%20or%20business%20class%20by%20finding%20just%20the%20right%20price%20for%20someone%20to%20splurge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZack%20Kass%2C%20an%20AI%20advisor%20and%20former%20head%20of%20go-to-market%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20rather%20than%20talk%20vaguely%20about%20how%20AI%20is%20boosting%20profits%2C%20companies%20need%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20they%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20improve%20the%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalk%20about%20how%20your%20wait%20time%20on%20customer%20support%20is%20coming%20down.%20Talk%20about%20how%20you're%20improving%20on%20time%20arrivals.%20Talk%20about%20how%20you're%20using%20AI%20to%20lose%20fewer%20bags%2C%26quot%3B%20Kass%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKass%20said%20many%20consumers%20might%20even%20approve%20of%20an%20airline%20charging%20wealthy%20passengers%2C%20like%20those%20who%20always%20opt%20for%20first-class%2C%20a%20bit%20more%20in%20order%20to%20provide%20lower%20prices%20to%20others.%20However%20AI%20is%20being%20used%20to%20improve%20the%20actual%20product%20or%20provide%20goods%20and%20services%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20incumbent%20on%20companies%20to%20tell%20that%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20individual%20companies%20talk%20about%20AI%20doesn't%20just%20impact%20their%20business%20either%2C%20Sanders%20said%2C%20but%20can%20also%20slow%20adoption%20across%20the%20board%20if%20it%20creates%20broader%20distrust%20among%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrust%20in%20AI%20arrives%20by%20a%20mule%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20leaves%20on%20a%20Maserati.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akvlamis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekvlamis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%40kelseyv.21%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-ai-pricing-backlash-shows-tightrope-companies-walk-ai-adoption-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754137741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%