t-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPunita%2C%20Manisha%20and%20Merlin%20have%20stayed%20together%20in%20times%20of%20joys%2C%20sorrows%20and%20everyday%20chapters%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunita%20Dadhich%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20journalist%20from%20Ahmedabad%2C%20was%20in%20fourth%20grade%20when%20she%20met%20Merlin%20and%20Manisha%20%E2%80%94%20two%20girls%20from%20her%20neighbourhood%20who%20would%20go%20on%20to%20become%20her%20closest%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20grew%20up%20together%2C%20sharing%20tiffins%2C%20cycling%20through%20the%20same%20lanes%2C%20and%20slowly%2C%20their%20lives%20began%20to%20intertwine%20beyond%20just%20childhood%20fun.%20But%20it%20was%20in%20life%E2%80%99s%20toughest%20chapters%20that%20their%20bond%20truly%20deepened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20class%2010%2C%20Manisha%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F461648%2Fshoojit-sircar-film-i-want-to-talk-starring-abishek-bachchan-based-on-real-life-story-of-arjun-sen-motivational-speaker-beat-cancer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elost%20her%20mother%20to%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20devastating%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punita%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20already%20like%20sisters%20by%20then%2C%20but%20after%20Aunty%20passed%20away%2C%20that%20bond%20only%20grew%20stronger.%20We%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20be%20there%20for%20lunch%20breaks%2C%20for%20festivals%2C%20for%20everything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20support%20continued%20through%20every%20milestone.%20When%20Manisha%20decided%20to%20marry%20the%20love%20of%20her%20life%20despite%20facing%20resistance%20from%20her%20family%2C%20Punita%20and%20Merlin%20stood%20by%20her%20side%2C%20never%20once%20doubting%20her%20choice.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20knew%20she%20was%20taking%20the%20right%20step.%20We%20got%20her%20married%2C%20and%20we%20were%20proud%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20years%20later%2C%20life%20has%20taken%20them%20in%20different%20directions.%20Merlin%20lives%20in%20Kerala.%20Manisha%20works%20and%20lives%20in%20the%20US%20with%20her%20partner.%20But%20the%20friendship%20still%20shows%20up%20in%20unexpected%20ways.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20surprised%20me%20at%20my%20office%20last%20December%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punita%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20seen%20them%20in%20so%20long.%20It%20felt%20like%20coming%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%2C%20what%20they%20share%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20being%20together%20in%20happy%20times.%20Instead%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20they%20held%20space%20for%20each%20other%20in%20grief%2C%20in%20transitions%2C%20and%20in%20everyday%20moments%20that%20make%20life%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20sparked%20by%20art%20in%20a%20park%2C%20a%20Facebook%20comment%2C%20or%20a%20shared%20lunch%20in%20school%2C%20these%20friendships%20remind%20us%20that%20the%20most%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387261%2Fsenior-citizens-travel-story-childhood-friendships-girls-trip-tourism-adventure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20meaningful%20bonds%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoften%20begin%20in%20the%20ordinary.%20As%20we%20grow%20older%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20loud%20declarations%2C%20but%20the%20soft%2C%20steady%20presence%20of%20a%20friend%20that%20often%20makes%20all%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754055000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T233342.337-1753985156.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Friendships%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20begin%20with%20a%20dramatic%20story.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20grow%20quietly%20on%20dance%20floors%2C%20badminton%20courts%2C%20or%20through%20a%20podcast%20mic.%20This%20Friendship%20Day%2C%20we%2