%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20sees%20a%20host%20of%20events%2C%20%3Cem%3Epujas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20celebrations%2C%20functions%20and%20events.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20an%20abandoned%20ruin%20whose%20magic%20was%20lost%20in%20the%20mists%20of%20time%2C%20this%2018th-century%20marvel%20has%20come%20to%20life%20once%20again.%20There%20is%20an%20innate%20sense%20of%20warmth%20within%20its%20walls%3B%20the%20events%20of%20the%20past%20decades%20are%20well%20behind%20it%3B%20there%20is%20only%20room%20for%20laughter%20and%20chatter%20now.%20The%20palace%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98white%E2%80%99%20seems%20to%20brighten%20with%20every%20passing%20day.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20as%20if%20it%20is%20saying%20%E2%80%98Thank%20You%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Pallab%20Roy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.getbengal.com%2Fdetails%2Fhow-a-zamindar-family-of-bengal-pioneered-royal-tourism%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20a%20zamindar%20family%20of%20Bengal%20pioneered%20Royal%20Tourism%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Gopa%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20Published%20on%2015%20January%202022.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754047800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479324%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nothing%20less%20than%20an%20Enid%20Blyton%20novel%2C%20the%20Roy%20family's%20journey%20to%20revisiting%20their%20ancestral%20palace%20in%20Kasim%20Bazar%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20finding%20it%20in%20a%20state%20of%20ruins%20and%20then%20restoring%20it%20to%20its%20former%20glory%2C%20will%20have%20you%20hooked.%20Visitors%20can%20now%20visit%20Cossimbazar%20Palace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479324%2Fcossimbazar-murshidabad-west-bengal-300-year-old-palace-roy-family%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Rs%201%20Cr%2B%20Cold-Pressed%20Oil%20Startup%20by%203%20Friends%20Is%20Boosting%20Farmer%20Incomes%20in%20Rajasthan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20January%202025%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELow%20wages%20and%20the%20relentless%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363341%2Fdelhi-police-constable-amit-lathia-teaches-underprivileged-low-income-children-for-competitive-exam-helps-get-govt-job%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecycle%20of%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%20force%20many%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan%20to%20leave%20their%20families%20and%20seek%20better%20opportunities%20elsewhere.%20Their%20children%2C%20innocent%20victims%20of%20circumstance%2C%20are%20often%20forced%20to%20discontinue%20their%20education.%20Three%20young%20entrepreneurs%2C%20Satyam%20Bhandari%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%2C%20and%20Mohit%20Rana%2C%20were%20determined%20to%20change%20this%2C%20and%20through%20grit%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20they%20founded%20Foreka%2C%20a%20company%20that%20aimed%20to%20empower%20these%20farmers%20and%20uplift%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20watched%20my%20mother%20struggle%20to%20become%20financially%20empowered%20so%20she%20could%20give%20me%20a%20better%20life%2C%20and%20that%20inspired%20me%20deeply.%20As%20I%20connected%20with%20farmers%20and%20tribals%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20her%20struggles.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%2C%20to%20ensure%20they%20too%20could%20have%20equal%20opportunities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Agastyamuni%2C%20a%20peaceful%20town%20cradled%20in%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20Satyam%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20father%20six%20days%20before%20he%20was%20born%2C%20had%20seen%20his%20mother%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20manage%20the%20household%20and%20raise%20him%20on%20her%20own.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20thankful%20to%20her%20for%20ensuring%20I%20attended%20a%20good%20school%20and%20for%20giving%20me%20everything%20I%20needed%20to%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20But%20many%20aren%E2%80%99t%20so%20lucky.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20passion%20to%20positively%20impact%20the%20lives%20of%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20schooling%2C%20he%20pursued%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20science%20(BSc)%20degree%20at%20a%20Dehradun%20college.%20Yearning%20to%20pursue%20some%20impactful%20work%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20Gandhi%20Fellowship%20in%202018-19%20%E2%80%94%20a%20life-changing%20decision%20that%20profoundly%20shaped%20his%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20here%20that%20I%20truly%20understood%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296633%2Fsocial-entrepreneur-quits-job-to-start-teach-children-through-art-nalandaway%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggles%20of%20marginalised%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20worked%20with%20the%20Piramal%20Foundation%20in%20Vidisha%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20witnessed%20the%20lives%20of%20farmers%20and%20tribal%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2027-year-old%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20teaching%20at%20a%20school%20where%20the%20attendance%20was%20consistently%20low.%20I%20later%20realised%20that%20the%20children%20were%20working%20in%20the%20fields%20or%20doing%20household%20chores%20because%20earning%20Rs%20100%20per%20day%20was%20far%20more%20important%20to%20their%20families%20than%20sending%20the%20children%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Fellowship%2C%20Satyam%20stayed%20with%20a%20tribal%20family%20in%20Vidisha%20district%20for%20a%20month.%20The%20head%20of%20the%20family%20was%20a%20painter%20who%20earned%20a%20modest%20income%2C%20and%20their%20livelihood%20largely%20depended%20on%20fieldwork.%20The%20elder%20son%2C%20just%20nine%20years%20old%2C%20was%20kept%20out%20of%20school%20to%20help%20in%20the%20fields%20and%20earn%20some%20money%20for%20a%20meal.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20six-year-old%20son%20cared%20for%20his%20younger%20sister%20and%20took%20on%20household%20chores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20family%20while%20an%20airplane%20flew%20overhead.%20I%20asked%20if%20they%20had%20ever%20travelled%20by%20flight%20or%20whether%20they%20planned%20to%2C%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20family%20responded%20that%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20in%20this%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20moment%20stayed%20with%20me%20and%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20harsh%20truth%20that%20survival%20often%20took%20precedence%20over%20education%20for%20many%20families%20in%20these%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20stay%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293576%2Fgramshree-helps-tribal-families-fight-middlemen-and-increase-farmer-earnings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20fellowship%20took%20him%20back%20to%20his%20childhood.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remembered%20how%20difficult%20it%20was%20for%20my%20mother%20to%20raise%20me%20without%20a%20father%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20life%20became%20easier%20after%20she%20secured%20a%20government%20job%2C%20I%20always%20knew%20how%20hard%20she%20worked%20to%20get%20us%20there.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202725px)%20100vw%2C%202725px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222725%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Satyam%20Bhandari%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%2C%20and%20Mohit%20Rana%20launched%20Foreka%20to%20help%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan%20earn%20their%20livelihood.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992.jpg%202725w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_4110-2_11zon-1735048992-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392173%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222044%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESatyam%20Bhandari%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%2C%20and%20Mohit%20Rana%20launched%20Foreka%20to%20help%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan%20earn%20their%20livelihood.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20that%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20children%20skipping%20school%20in%20these%20areas%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20absence%20of%20will%2C%20but%20the%20absence%20of%20resources.%20%E2%80%9CBasic%20needs%20like%20food%20and%20shelter%20were%20prioritised%20over%20education.%20I%20understood%20that%20creating%20livelihoods%20for%20these%20communities%20was%20the%20key%20to%20unlocking%20their%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20understanding%20became%20the%20foundation%20for%20his%20future%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20talking%20to%20local%20farmers%2C%20listening%20to%20their%20problems%2C%20and%20figuring%20out%20what%20could%20be%20done%20to%20help%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20fellowship%2C%20he%20continued%20probing%20the%20causes%20that%20led%20to%20farmers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247044%2Fias-hero-parikipandla-narahari-madhya-pradesh-upsc-exam-student-mentor-ladli-laxmi-yojana-indore-inspiring-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efacing%20financial%20struggles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Satyam%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20moment%20came%20after%20he%20met%20Geeta%20Devi%2C%20a%20tribal%20woman%20who%20had%20risen%20from%20poverty%20to%20become%20the%20director%20of%20a%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisation%20(FPO).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20journey%20was%20incredibly%20inspiring.%20She%20had%20once%20struggled%20just%20to%20buy%20tea%20leaves%2C%20but%20now%20she%20was%20managing%20an%20FPO%20that%20empowered%20farmers.%20Her%20story%20gave%20me%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20right%20resources%2C%20anybody%20can%20rise%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20went%20beyond%20just%20supporting%20farmers.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20have%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20from%20cultivation%20to%20sales%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20young%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20fellowship%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20hometown%20where%20he%20discussed%20his%20desire%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20with%20his%20schoolmates%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%20and%20Mohit%20Rana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20college%2C%20we%20used%20to%20talk%20about%20doing%20business%20together.%20Whenever%20we%20saw%20farmers%20working%20so%20hard%2C%20we%20thought%20about%20how%20they%20struggle%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20says%20Mohit%2C%20who%20has%20an%20engineering%20background%20and%20was%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20working%20as%20a%20civil%20engineer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20friends%20got%20together%20to%20take%20the%20entrepreneurial%20plunge%20and%20founded%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20inspiration%20to%20join%20this%20venture%20stemmed%20from%20a%20deep%20desire%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F254622%2Flenovo-technology-agastya-international-meghshala-door-step-school-technoserve-medha-social-impact-innovation-oniline-education-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20people%20in%20rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20want%20to%20stay%20with%20their%20families%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood.%20I%20wanted%20to%20empower%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rohit%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20sales%20and%20operations%2C%20Mohit%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20co-found%20the%20venture%2C%20focused%20on%20sourcing%20raw%