es%20and%20sustainable%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%20The%20setup%20includes%20cold-pressed%20machines%20owned%20by%20the%20farmers%2C%20while%20Foreka%20works%20on%20a%20co-profit%20model%2C%20sharing%2050%25%20of%20the%20profits%20after%20covering%20costs.%20Partnering%20with%20two%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%2C%20one%20near%20Jhansi%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20Chambal%20Valley%2C%20Foreka%20sources%20groundnuts%2C%20processes%20them%2C%20and%20sells%20groundnut%20oil.%20The%20model%20helps%20reduce%20outmigration%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20local%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Their%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F