%2Ftamil-nadu-dumpyard-mini-forest-compost-waste-organic-vegetables-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelps%20forests%20grow%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20just%20two%20to%20three%20years%20instead%20of%20decades.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20envisioned%20a%20green%20belt.%20To%20keep%20the%20plants%20alive%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20gardener%20and%20installed%20solar%20water%20pumps%20to%20save%20electricity%20while%20watering%20the%20saplings.%20We%20also%20cleaned%20one%20of%20the%20two%20water%20bodies.%20Now%20cleared%20of%20refuse%2C%20the%20pond%20is%20harvesting%20rainwater%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rains%20arrived%2C%20the%20newly%20planted%20saplings%20thrived%2C%20breathing%20life%20into%20the%20once-neglected%20patch%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20community%20support%2C%20SAFE%20levelled%20the%20land%20to%20fix%20the%20illegal%20mining%20pits%20and%20prepare%20the%20site%20for%20tree%20planting.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477276%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20community%20support%2C%20SAFE%20levelled%20the%20land%20to%20fix%20the%20illegal%20mining%20pits%20and%20prepare%20the%20site%20for%20tree%20planting.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20locals%20become%20guardians%20of%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20project%20didn%E2%80%99t%20rest%20on%20Vikrant%20alone.%20He%20is%20quick%20to%20credit%20the%20community%20for%20sparking%20and%20sustaining%20this%20change.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20community%20that%20first%20identified%20and%20alerted%20me%20about%20the%20problem.%20Now%2C%20they%20remain%20vigilant.%20They%20report%20to%20me%20directly%20if%20they%20see%20any%20trucks%20trying%20to%20dump%20waste%2C%20or%20when%20the%20gardener%20is%20on%20leave%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20most%20dedicated%20guardians%20is%20Antram.%20He%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20protect%20the%20site%20from%20further%20harm.%20He%20watches%20over%20the%20spot%2C%20ensuring%20no%20one%20contaminates%20it%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20come%20here%20to%20plant%20trees.%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20check%20that%20no%20cattle%20damage%20them.%20With%20the%20rain%2C%20the%20trees%20look%20lush%20and%20green.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20garbage%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20no%20unpleasant%20odour.%20It%E2%80%99s%20refreshing%20now.%20Customers%20can%20now%20sit%20at%20my%20stall%20without%20foul%20smells%20bothering%20them.%20My%20business%20is%20also%20doing%20well%20because%20people%20are%20more%20willing%20to%20visit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20easy.%20Early%20funding%20rejections%20were%20disheartening%2C%20and%20convin