natural%20farming%20techniques%20while%20preserving%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%20then%20automatically%20the%20seed%20germination%20value%2C%20and%20preservation%20and%20techniques%20of%20germination%2C%20will%20last%20longer%20and%20plants%20from%20these%20seeds%20will%20sustain%20through%20natural%20calamities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%20300%20farmers%20in%20seed%20preservation%20techniques.%20But%2C%20the%20legacy%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseed%20preservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20region%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20with%20him%2C%20he%20insists.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20an%20ongoing%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Darlapudi%20Ravi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiucn.org%2Fpress-release%2F202410%2Fmore-one-three-tree-species-worldwide-faces-extinction-iucn-red-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20one%20in%20three%20tree%20species%20worldwide%20faces%20extinction%20%E2%80%93%20IUCN%20Red%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20IUCN%2C%20Published%20on%2028%20October%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsii.in%2Fimportance-of-seed-banks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImportance%20of%20Seed%20Banks%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Federation%20of%20Seed%20Industry%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753965000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-2-1732015773.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479175%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20was%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%20at%20a%20cement%20industry%20when%20he%20realised%20how%20modern%20dietary%20practices%20lead%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20diseases.%20Here's%20how%20this%20realisation%20motivated%20him%20to%20build%20a%20seed%20bank.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479175%2Fseed-preservation-andhra-pradesh-darlapudi-ravi-indigenous-local-varieties-2%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20New%20York%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Love%20Letter%20to%20Indian%20Cooking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20October%20202%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20last%20day%20of%20Navratri%2C%20the%20Hindu%20festival%20celebrated%20with%20great%20pomp%20and%20splendour%20over%20nine%20nights.%20The%20fireworks%20outside%20my%20window%20oblige%20with%20drumrolls%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20an%20evening%20I%20will%20remember%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20few%20seconds%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359321%2Fvikas-khanna-chef-journey-success-story-masterchef-michelin-star-bungalow-restaurant-new-york-amritsar-india-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVikas%20Khanna%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20internet%E2%80%99s%20beloved%20chef%20%E2%80%94%20takes%20a%20few%20seconds%20to%20unmute%20his%20mic%20and%20adjust%20his%20camera%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20clear%20view%20of%20him%20in%20his%20elegant%20New%20York%20City%20home%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20smile%20at%20this%20%E2%80%98pinch-me%E2%80%99%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20from%20the%20outset%2C%20Khanna%20is%20chipper%3B%20no%20one%20(except%20probably%20the%20general%20manager%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%2C%20Sameer%20Bhatt)%20would%20guess%20he%20has%20pulled%20an%20all-nighter.%20Well%20into%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%2C%20Khanna%20was%20attempting%20to%20replicate%20the%20intricate%20wings%20of%20a%20peacock%E2%80%99s%20feathers%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20sweet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20decades%20of%20culinary%20experience%20ensured%20he%20aced%20the%20task.%20And%20now%20for%20replicating%20the%20same%20onto%20a%20hundred-odd%20pieces!%20Known%20to%20push%20the%20envelope%2C%20Khanna%20does%20justice%20to%20this%20reputation%20when%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20each%20feather%20to%20be%20exactly%20alike.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20how%20the%20plumage%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandirs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temples)%20in%20Indian%20homes%2C%20Khanna%20was%20keen%20that%20every%20guest%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20his%20dream%20restaurant%20project%20launched%20in%20New%20York%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20return%20home%20that%20day%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288997%2Fpunjabi-wrestler-harbans-vig-invented-indias-loved-dhodha-barfi-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebox%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spot%20the%20delicate%20%3Cem%3Emor%20pankh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(peacock%20feather)%2C%20and%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875.jpg%5C%22%